      "para_id": "Q004842.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) E-ana-tum , child of Aya-kurgal , ruler of Lagaš , bought a garden with an area of 1 bur and 2 iku from the brother of Amar-egala , the travelling merchant . He paid 2 mana silver for him . The gift was 1 pot of beer ."
    }
  ],
